text: Yury Golovshchikov (born 10 July 1963) is a Soviet ski jumper. He competed in the normal hill and large hill events at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of the Soviet Union Category:Ski jumpers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saint Petersburg
